helptext.en:
This is where you can record all the observations you make of a particular building on the easement property.

Because some easements have multiple buildings to inspect, you can add as many buildings as you need. In the "Building Name" field, identify which building being observed.

Enter observations for Roofs & Chimneys and each Facade.
